{% comment %}
  PRNTD — Immersive Homepage
  Rebrand v4 — February 2026
  Inspired by: Juun.J Persona campaign page
  
  Structure:
  1. Full-screen hero with circular reveal interaction (UNTOUCHED)
  2. Campaign statement — massive typography, clean editorial
  3. Full-bleed editorial image with overlaid text
  4. Collection highlights — asymmetric editorial grid
  5. Brand manifesto — text over texture/detail image
  6. All Looks — horizontal scroll lookbook
  7. Archive — previous collections
  8. Full footer
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %} ============================================================
   SECTION 1: IMMERSIVE HERO (unchanged)
   ============================================================ {% endcomment %}

